---
title: Quick Chermoula Chicken with Zhoug Couscous and Veggies
description: A recipe to spice up your weeknights, the Chermoula-spiced chicken is teamed with fluffy couscous mixed with zhoug. Zhoug is a bright, spicy sauce made from coriander, chilli and pesto and it is great with the sweeter, more fragrant flavouring of chermoula.
